<br>
But I general swear back at those folks and move on.<br>
<br>
When it comes to PvP for me, the only thing I don't like is camping. If your just standing there I will PvP you, unless you shout out that your not hostile. I will leave you to your oats a grain. <br>
<br>
One of my biggest annoyances(All be it one I take risk upon myself for.) Is going to a missoin thrue a 25% zone.<br>
I have had people kill me even though I have a macro set that is screaming /shout I am not hostile! Running mission! Please dont' attack! And summarily got creamed 5 times thrue the Whompa or grid in that next hour.<br>
<br>
And then I had one very gentlmanly character fly over in his Yalmha and ask me why I was standing over by a mountain of rocks (Stret east bank) and buffing? He apparently thought I was prepairing to dive into the PvP.<br>
But even with me delaying my answer because I didn't realize he was there he waited and asked again. I told him that I was going to a mission and was buffing simply to have a fighting chance with the MOBs out here.<br>
He took my answer for what it was, told me he would be watching me and several days later I met him again and he both had several Martial Arts duels as we had continuasly stayed in lvl range of each other.(BTW he won every match. He said he was twinked into implants and armors that I was lacking myself very much. He even said with out those helping items I did well against him. (Got him down to 1/4 his life each time.)<br>
<br>
All in all I have had many pleasant PVP matches.<br>
<br>
Another comes to mind. Where in MMD I got beat by an Omni Agent complemented her skill and moved on. Later on I went Omni myself and met an alternate character of hers by happinstance at a mission term. She gave me a 3 hour tour of Omni territory since I hadn't been there before. <br>
<br>
All those horrible stories people tell sometimes seem like loads of wind to me. ^_^ <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.showMessageRange?topicID=6.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=6.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.showNextMessage?topicID=6.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=26><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.emailToFriend?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.threadControl?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"